    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>整理一下经常忘记的mysql命令</p>

<h1>连接</h1>

<p><code>
$ mysql -u root -p
</code></p>

<h1>list</h1>

<p><code>
$ show DATABASES;
$ show TABLES;
</code></p>

<h1>Error</h1>

<ul>
<li>ERROR 1045 (28000): Access denied for user &lsquo;root&rsquo;@&lsquo;localhost&rsquo; (using password: YES)</li>
</ul>


<p><code>
$ mysqld --skip-grant-tables
$ mysql -u root mysql
$ mysql&gt; UPDATE user SET Password=PASSWORD('my_password') where USER='root';
$ mysql&gt; FLUSH PRIVILEGES;
</code></p>
